Privacy Policy - BrainyOff – AI SEO & ASO Chat
Last Updated: February 10, 2025
Introduction
Welcome to BrainyOff – AI SEO & ASO Chat ("we," "our," or "app"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our offline AI chat management application.
Information We Collect
Local Storage Data
Chat conversations and message history
User preferences and settings
AI model configurations
Custom prompts and templates
Chat categories and organization structures
Device Information
Device type and model
Operating system version
Storage usage statistics
Application performance metrics
All data is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to external servers.
How We Use Your Information
Local Processing
Managing and organizing chat conversations
Implementing user preferences
Optimizing app performance
Providing offline AI chat functionality
Organizing and categorizing conversations
Data Security
Local Security Measures
End-to-end encryption for stored conversations
Secure local database implementation
Optional passcode/biometric protection
Regular security updates and patches
Data Sharing and Transfer
We do not collect or transmit data to external servers. Your information remains completely local to your device.
User Rights and Controls
Delete any or all stored conversations
Export your data in common formats
Modify app permissions
Update or change privacy settings
Control data retention periods
Children's Privacy
Our app does not knowingly collect or store information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal information within the app, please contact us to have it removed.
Offline Operation
App functions completely offline
No internet connection required
No background data transmission
Optional features requiring internet will be clearly marked
Contact Information
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your privacy rights, please contact us at:
Email: ai-chat@asospy.com
Website: www.asospy.com/privacy
Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Users will be notified of any significant changes through the app. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.